"PI699E2.8P43A-3 REV1.0" is silkscreened on the board. :This is a ''[[Shenzhen Gongjin Electronics]] ([[SGE]])'' P/N.
It is likely this [http://www.twsz.com/en/product/67/267.html 500Mbps Nano Powerline Wall Mount Adapter]. :Has a ''LNK623DG'' AC/DC Switching Converter.
This product actually supports 500Mbps PHY rates over powerlines. :The manual and QIG for the device are dated 2013-01-07.
